# Threat Hunting: `Analzing the mal activities`
- Process of investing sign of malicious activities, anomalies & analysing patterns or events to find threats in the system.

- eg. Unusual network behaviour, app using high resources 

- `EDR > Hunting > Events` > Filter out based on Type (file, registry, network, process)
- eg. process.image.path:recycle.bin
- eg. mitre.attack.tactic.name:"Execution"

> Precreated `Advanced Hunting` queries: can be cloned or run